overview: The National headlined at Ypsigrock Festival in Castelbuono, Sicily, Italy in 2019.  The concert was shared as part of the band's "Exciting Communal Event series", which launched with a stream of their show at Primavera Sound in summer 2018.  The Ypsigrock Festival performance took place in association with The Independent, which hosted the festival's main stage.
title: The National - Live From Ypsigrock 2019
